-- Romania Utility Calls for Arges Water-Treatment Work Bids
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2013-02-25T11:25:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-25/romania-utility-calls-for-arges-water-treatment-work-bids.html
The Romanian water utility  Apa Canal
2000 SA  is seeking bids for water-treatment works in the
southern county of Arges under a contract valued at 27.7 million
lei ($8.4 million).  Bids are due April 11 for the 21-month contract, which
includes waste improvements for the towns of Costesti, Budeasa,
Merisani, Mosoaia, Pitesti, Stefanesti and Topoloveni, according
to a Feb. 23 European Union  procurement statement .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  